org.regenstrief.ucum
Class DimensionedQuantity

java.lang.Object
  org.regenstrief.ucum.DimensionedQuantity
Direct Known Subclasses:
Unit
public class DimensionedQuantity
extends java.lang.Object

This class implements a physical quantity. - REAL magnitude - Dimension dimension where Dimension is essentially a vector of exponents of the base units. This class does not, however, preserve any sense of "original unit", i.e., the value of this class is always in canonical form.
